dc_title_s: Brazil--south coast, Port of Itajaí (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: reproduction of Brazilian Chart 1801, 4th edition, April 15, 1990 ... with the Brazilian Directorate of Hydrography and Navigation. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "From Brazilian surveys to 1987." "Brazilian copyright law applies." "Soundings in meters." Includes survey listing and tidal information. Map No.24131 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. Diretoria de Hidrografia e Navegação. Defense Mapping Agency
